<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-10580] Conditionally initialized `final` variables considered maybe uninitialized</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-10580</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running the following in `groovyConsole`:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
final &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; i
final &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; a = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (a) {
    i = 1
} &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; IllegalStateException(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;a is &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
}
println &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;i = $i&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;would give me:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;1 compilation error:
The variable [i] may be uninitialized
. At [9:15] at line: 9, column: 15
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems groovyc does not take throwing an exception as a non-reachable branch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This code is almost a verbatim copy from a java code that is working.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This looks similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-8472&quot; title=&quot;Final variable analysis doesn&amp;#39;t account for early exit for try/catch/finally&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-8472&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-8472&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and a few others.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
