                            <comment id="17521401" author="paulk" created="Wed, 13 Apr 2022 01:00:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added code tags. Plus here is a JavaShell snippet to confirm the Java behaviour:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; js = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; org.apache.groovy.util.JavaShell()
js.run(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;Main&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, &apos;&apos;&apos;
public &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Main {
  public static void main(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;[] args) {
    final &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; i;
    final &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; a = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (a) {
        i = 1;
    } &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; IllegalStateException(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a is &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
    }
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;.out.println(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;i = &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + i);
  }
}
&apos;&apos;&apos;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17521416" author="paulk" created="Wed, 13 Apr 2022 02:08:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The same behavior is observed with the branches reversed or with returns instead of throws:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (a) {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; IllegalStateException(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;a is &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
} &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
    i = 1
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Looking at the codebase, it appears we are only looking for returns/throws for try/catch and switch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
